~ start
You walk through brambles and ferns as you head off a dusty trail into the woods, your guard up. Not even an hour ago, you were instructed by your work to speak with a client who lives in a hut just outside of town. While your work as a courier did take you to many places, none were as daunting as this. As you passed by looming shadows and darted your eyes to every small movement in your peripheral, you prayed that whoever this was wouldn’t make you go too far. 
# show outside of place
Slowly, you sense warmth coming from just ahead. A decently sized hut stands before you. Seemingly out of place in this barren area that leads towards the woods. While the hut seems standard in shape and color, its placement still perplexes you. The owner could have placed it anywhere, but why here? But knowing who your client is, you understand that things like this will probably be common in the coming days. You step inside.
do enter_hut()
The room before you is large, very large, larger than the hutt should have space for. Decorated with various pieces of furniture and decorations you’ve never seen before. There are also hallways that seemingly connect to other rooms. You call out but receive no answer. The client said they would be here, it's just a matter of when they’ll show up.  You look around at the decorations that adorn the room. There are various paintings that depict lands and skies you’ve never seen before, some barren, some plentiful with life. You walk closer to a painting that depicts a dazzling ocean. 
