The room, once adorned with various paintings, is now adorned with trophies of various animals. Some you recognize while others are beyond your wildest dreams. You then notice the furniture has also changed. Now, two couches are settled with a large coffee table between them and a hearth settled in the wall off to the side.
???: Take a seat. 
